name: Tundra Bundle
description:
Join the Elite 26th Legion with the new TSF Tundra Deployment Pack.

Featured within:
[color=#00ffff]Tundra Armor (male and female)
Tundra Exosuit
Tundra Axe
Tundra Welder
Tundra Rifle
Tundra Shotgun
Tundra Flamethrower
Tundra Grenade Launcher
Tundra Heavy Machinegun
Tundra Command Station
Tundra Extractor
Tundra Shoulder Patch[/color]

Equip the pack today and take the fight to the enemy!

name: Tundra Armor
description: Fighting the Kharaa threat takes skill and cunning. TSF Tundra Armor has been designed to withstand the toughest battles.  Equip the TSF Tundra Armor today and fight for the 26th Legion!

name: Tundra Exosuit
description: On the battlefield, you need the best load-out for the job, and a paint job to match. The new TSF Tundra Exosuit Armor has been designed to withstand the largest Kharaa attacks. Adapt to survive, equip the TSF Tundra Exo-Armor today!

name: Tundra Rifle
description: When in combat with the Kharaa, you need both function and style. The TSF Tundra Rifle is designed to provide the best of both in war-torn, dank environments.

name: Tundra Shotgun
description: The most destructive close-combat weapon in the TSF arsenal just got even better. Deal a cold harsh blow to the enemy with the TSF Tundra Shotgun.

name: Tundra Shoulder Patch
description: To show they have battled in the fiercest environments, the TSF Marines place upon their shoulders the TSF Tundra shoulder patch. A patch of honor, for those who endure vigorous warfare.

name: Kodiak Armor
description: Aliens will be no match for the specialized TSF Kodiak Armor. Equip to take the fight to the Kharaa on their terms!

name: Kodiak Exosuit
description: The TSF fight in all environments against the vicious Kharaa threat. The TSF Kodiak Exosuit Armor is both practical and environmentally friendly. Just not for the Kharaa.

name: Kodiak Rifle
description: Forged to fight in the most rugged of environments, the TSF Kodiak Rifle is outfitted to bring peace and order to the galaxy.

name: Kodiak Shoulder Patch
description: Alterra Mining Corp's latest and most technologically advanced TSF Kodiak shoulder patch.

name: Kodiak Skulk
description: Evolve or die, the Kharaa come in all forms. Focus & stay sharp, or you might miss this breed of Skulk.

description:

Reaper Egg[/color]

name: Reaper Shoulder Patch
description: They say Death stalks us all. With the TSF Reaper shoulder patch, Death comes with you into battle.

name: Reaper Skulk
description: Anaemic but deadly, the Reaper Skulk is more deadly than it's ghostly looks. Don't be fooled, it's not an apparition.

name: Reaper Gorge
description: Sickly in looks, mucid by nature. Fighting against the Reaper Gorge's clammy skin is not for the queasy.

name: Reaper Lerk
description: Ghostly and ghoulish, the Reaper Lerk sends cold chills running down the spine of any TSF Marine that wishes to socialize.

name: Reaper Fade
description: Chilling and ominous... Don't blink, the Reaper Fade might just be the last thing you see before Death itself.

name: Reaper Onos
description: As if from some Demonic sanctum, the Reaper Onos gores fear into the heart of any adversary.

name: Shadow Bundle
description:
Become the phantom that creeps in the Shadows, with the Shadow Bundle.

Featured within:
[color=#ff7e3e]Shadow Skulk
Shadow Fade
Shadow Onos
Shadow Hive
Shadow Harvester
Shadow Tunnel
Shadow Egg[/color]

name: Elite Assault Armor
description: Fighting as part of the Elite Reinforcement Squad, members are bestowed Elite Assault Armor and put heavy pressure on the Kharaa threat

name: Shadow Shoulder Patch
description: Checking your corners is basic TSF Marine 101 good practice. Checking the shadows is much more dangerous. Declare ownership of the shadows with the TSF Shadow shoulder patch.

name: Shadow Skulk
description: In the darkest corners of abandoned space stations, the Shadow Skulk waits. Stay together, or you might become its next delightful meal.

name: Shadow Gorge
description: In gloomy darkness, the Shadow Gorge will build its nest. Watch out for Shadow Babblers, Hydras, and Clogs! No flash pictures, please.

name: Shadow Lerk
description: The sound of unholy flapping will spell doom to those who ignore it. The Shadow Lerk requires a sharp eye and a quick trigger to take it down.

name: Shadow Fade
description: During battle, frightening sounds echo through the halls. Beware, the Shadow Fade practices its terror on the unsuspecting marine.

name: Shadow Onos
description: If there is one Kharaa to give an aura of foreboding, it's the Shadow Onos. Look alive, or you'll be departed of this life in no time.

name: Shadow Onos
description: If there is one Kharaa to give an aura of foreboding, it's the Shadow Onos. Look alive, or you'll be departed of this life in no time.

name: Deluxe Armor
description: For those in the TSF Forces who want to stand out from the crowd, the TSF Deluxe Armor provides absolutely zero benefit from standard-issue TSF Armor. Except you look like a badass. Be a badass.

name: Assault Armor
description: The TSF Marine's armor research team has developed the 'Assault Armor' for use in heavy conflict with the Kharaa threat.

name: Reinforced Shoulder Patch
description: Why buy government war bonds when you can wear the Reinforced shoulder patch? Bet on the TSF Marines and show your support!

name: Abyss Bundle
description:
Featured Within:

Abyss Skulk
Abyss Gorge (Babbler, Hydra, Clog)
Abyss Lerk
Abyss Fade
Abyss Onos
Abyss Hive
Abyss Harvester
Abyss Tunnel
Abyss Egg

name: Abyss Skulk
description: Caged in the coldest corners of the facility, the Abyss Skulk stalks its prey. Be afraid, as you might be its next dessert.

name: Abyss Gorge
description: In Origin's labs, scientists have discovered a phenotype of the Kharaa rarely seen, the Abyss genetic marker. They are unsure of what causes this mutation in the species but warn it's not to be taken lightly, especially when a Gorge takes on this form. Stay alert marines.

name: Abyss Lerk
description: First appearing in the streets of Metro, the Abyss Lerk can strike from anywhere.

name: Skull 'n' Crossfire
description: Who needs fire and brimstone when you have the TSF 'Skull 'n' Crossfire' Rifle? Made from real Skulk skull paint, adorn yourself and blaze your way to victory!

name: NS2WC14 Globe Shoulder Patch
description: One of the great battles during the Kharaa War of 2014, the NS2WC14 Globe shoulder patch exudes support for the war effort.

name: Godar Shoulder Patch
description: European descended Legions in the TSF credit the bygone 'Godar' battalion for their battle-hardened egos from the First Kharaa War. A show of the Godar shoulder patch is a show of respect to the venerable heroes.

name: Saunamen Shoulder Patch
description: Battalion descended from Finnish bloodlines, the Saunamen shoulder patch is the TSF approved digital towel. Never leave the barracks without it.

name: Snails Shoulder Patch
description: The mighty Snail is often thought of as a slow creature. The Legendary Snails battalion are hailed as anything but. Undeniable Francophiles, the show of a Snails shoulder patch in battle is a show of fine exquisite warfare.

name: Titus Gaming Shoulder Patch
description: Loud and proud, the Titus Gaming shoulder patch is worn by those descended from the old North American continent. Worn with honor and pride, the Titans of History seep through this shoulder patch.

name: Eat Your Greens Shoulder Patch
description: Getting your toes wet, a shoulder decal is what you get!

name: The Pumpkin Patch
description: When the wind is chilled and the moon is bright, the Pumpkin Patch will stir up a fright.

name: Leviathan Shoulder Patch
description: Celebrating Subnautica's release, remind your enemies what terror looks like with the Reaper Leviathan.

name: Peeper Shoulder Patch
description: Celebrating Subnautica's release, splash around the battlefield with this playful Peeper.

name: Summer Gorge Patch
description: Stay chilled-out this summer with the coolest Gorge shoulder patch on the warfront.

name: The Haunted Babbler Shoulder Patch
description: When the wind is chilled and the moon is bright, the Haunted Babbler will stir up a fright.

name: Nocturne Skulk
description: Marines have the boogeyman; aliens have the Nocturne skulk.

name: Nocturne Gorge
description: Incapacitate your enemies with blinding cuteness!

name: Nocturne Lerk
description: The sound of a Nocturne lerk's approach will give goosebumps to even the most experienced marines and that's only when it wants to be heard.

name: Nocturne Fade
description: Every full moon, the nocturn fade comes out to hunt.  It also comes out to hunt every non-full moon night as well.

name: Nocturne Onos
description: The pain of being gored to death is only made worse by how spooky the horn is.

name: Forge Bundle
description:
Forge your destiny!
Show the enemy fire cleans filth with the Forge skin pack.

Featured within:
[color=#0fbae5]Forge Armor (Male and Female)
Forge Axe
Forge Welder
Forge Rifle

Forge Shotgun

Forge Command Station
Forge Extractor[/color]

name: Forge Armor
description: Display the quite literal heat of battle for all to see! Aliens tremble at the sight of marines who don't understand how metaphors work.

name: Forge Rifle
description: Superior TSF design means shell casings are 7% hotter when ejected!

name: Forge Pistol
description: A shipment of TSF pistols from the weapon manufacturing planet of XDM-5 came with a defective safety.  No worries, we'll just give em a slick coat of paint and call it a feature!

name: Forge Axe
description: Top TSF science-doing people have theorized that a red axe can be swung faster and harder.  Help them test their theory!

name: Forge Exosuit
description: Tired of the usual chilly exosuit cockpit?  The Forge exosuit takes care of that.  Now 40% toastier!

name: Forge Shotgun
description: Fire and brimstone have nothing on this devastating weapon. Bring the heat of war with the TSF Forge Shotgun.

name: Forge Flamethrower
description: Spark victory with the TSF Forge Flamethrower. Red hot to the touch, red hot in look.

name: Black Armor
description: Almost legendary, the members of this Elite Fighting Force were the first to fight in the new wave of the Kharaa Wars. The TSF Black Armor is only worn by the most dedicated and battle-hardened of all the marines.

name: Unearthed
description:
A new form of Kharaa has revealed itself from the crystal mines of Unearthed. Mesmerize both friend and foe with these alien structure skins.
